#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&plasma; provides a modern and customizable environment for running your "
"favorite applications and accessing your information wherever it may be. "
"Other common attributes of the &plasma; Desktop include advanced window "
"management and desktop effects, support for &kde; &plasma; Widgets, "
"integrated search, hardware management and a high degree of customizability."
msgstr ""
"&plasma; zagotavlja sodobno in prilagodljivo okolje za zagon priljubljenih "
"aplikacij in dostop do informacij, ne glede na to, kje se nahajajo. Druge "
"skupne lastnosti namizja &plasma; vključujejo napredno upravljanje oken in "
"učinke namizja, podporo za pripomočke &kde; &plasma;, integrirano iskanje, "
"upravljanje strojne opreme in visoko stopnjo prilagodljivosti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &plasma;"
msgstr "Uporaba &plasma;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "&plasma; Components"
msgstr "&plasma; Sestavine"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "&plasma; Widgets and Containments"
msgstr "&plasma; Pripomočki in vsebniki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "The essence of &plasma; revolves around two basic concepts:"
msgstr "Bistvo sistema &plasma; se vrti okoli dveh osnovnih konceptov:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "&plasma; Widgets"
msgstr "&plasma; Pripomočki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Applets, or small applications that live on the desktop."
msgstr "\"Appleti\" ali majhne aplikacije, ki živijo na namizju."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Containments</term>"
msgstr "<term>Vsebniki</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "Applets that act as the container for the &plasma; widgets"
msgstr "Majhne aplikacije, ki delujejo kot vsebnik za &plasma; gradnike"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On a default desktop, there are two main elements: the Panel and the Desktop "
"itself. Both are containments in the &plasma; sense."
msgstr ""
"Na privzetem namizju sta dva glavna elementa: plošča in namizje. Oba sta "
"vsebnika v smislu &plasma;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default &plasma; Desktop"
msgstr "Privzeto &plasma; Namizje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &plasma; Desktop can be configured in countless ways. The screenshot "
"seen below shows a fairly standard desktop. Some distributions apply "
"extensive customizations, so your desktop may look different."
msgstr ""
"Namizje &plasma; lahko konfigurirate na nešteto načinov. Spodnji posnetek "
"zaslona prikazuje dokaj standardno namizje. Nekatere distribucije "
"uporabljajo obsežne prilagoditve, zato bo vaše namizje morda videti drugače."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Similarly, the graphical appearance of the interface elements can be styled. "
"These screenshots uses the &plasma; default style, Breeze."
msgstr ""
"Podobno je mogoče oblikovati tudi grafični videz elementov vmesnika. Na teh "
"posnetkih je uporabljen privzeti slog &plasma; Sapica."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "A fairly standard &plasma; Desktop"
msgstr "Dokaj standardna &plasma; Namizje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The program starter. Usually this will be <link linkend=\"panel-launcher"
"\">Application Launcher</link>."
msgstr ""
"Zaganjalnik programa. Običajno je to <link linkend=\"panel-launcher"
"\">Zaganjalnik aplikacij</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "A couple of icons giving easy access to often used applications"
msgstr ""
"Nekaj ikon, ki omogočajo enostaven dostop do pogosto uporabljenih aplikacij"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <link linkend=\"panel-taskbar\">Task Manager</link>, which shows the "
"titles of windows belonging to the applications currently running. No "
"application had opened a window, when the screenshot was taken"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"panel-taskbar\">Upravitelj opravil</link>, ki prikazuje "
"naslove oken trenutno zagnanih aplikacij. Ko je bil posnet posnetek zaslona, "
"ni bilo odprto nobeno okno aplikacije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <link linkend=\"panel-system-tray\">System Tray</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"panel-system-tray\">Sistemski pladenj</link>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <link linkend=\"panel-digital-clock\">Digital Clock</link> widget"
msgstr "Gradnik <link linkend=\"panel-digital-clock\">Digitalna ura</link>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <link linkend=\"panel-toolbox\">Panel Toolbox</link>"
msgstr "Orodje <link linkend=\"panel-toolbox\">Zbirka orodij za ploščo</link>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <link linkend=\"desktop\">Desktop</link> Toolbox"
msgstr "Zbirka orodij <link linkend=\"desktop\">Namizje</link>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid "A Folder View widget, showing the content of the Desktop folder"
msgstr "Gradnik Pogled mape, ki prikazuje vsebino mape namizja"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Panel"
msgstr "Pult"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The default panel holds a few &plasma; widgets: starting from the left, "
"there is the application launcher."
msgstr ""
"Privzeta plošča vsebuje nekaj pripomočkov &plasma;: na levi strani je "
"zaganjalnik aplikacij."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid "Application Launcher"
msgstr "Zaganjalnik aplikacij"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Application launcher</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Zaganjalnik aplikacij</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Application launcher</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Zaganjalnik aplikacij</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use it to start applications, open recently opened files and the "
"usual logout/shutdown options. There is also a structure that allows you to "
"browse through your applications. The layout has been optimized for the use "
"case that is most common: starting an application. The default tab is the "
"<guilabel>Favorites</guilabel> tab that holds the most-used entries. In the "
"beginning, you'll probably find yourself using the <guilabel>Applications</"
"guilabel> tab more often. Once you have found out what your most frequently "
"started applications are, <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on the "
"items and select the <guimenuitem>Add to Favorites</guimenuitem> to add them "
"to your <guilabel>Favorites</guilabel> (or directly into the panel or on the "
"desktop. Note that you need to <quote>unlock</quote> &plasma; by means of "
"<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> clicking on the desktop for any kind of "
"modification)."
msgstr ""
"Z njim lahko zaženete aplikacije, odprete nedavno odprte datoteke in "
"uporabite običajne možnosti odjave/izklopa. Na voljo je tudi struktura, ki "
"omogoča brskanje po aplikacijah. Postavitev je optimizirana za najpogostejši "
"primer uporabe: zagon aplikacije. Privzeti zavihek je zavihek "
"<guilabel>Priljubljene</guilabel>, ki vsebuje najpogosteje uporabljene "
"vnose. Na začetku boste verjetno pogosteje uporabljali zavihek "
"<guilabel>Aplikacije</guilabel>. Ko ugotovite, kateri so vaši najpogosteje "
"zagnani programi, <mousebutton>desno</mousebutton> kliknite elemente in "
"izberite <guimenuitem>Dodaj v priljubljene</guimenuitem>, da jih dodate v "
"<guilabel>Priljubljene</guilabel> (ali neposredno v ploščo ali na namizje. "
"Upoštevajte, da morate <quote>odkleniti</quote> &plasma; z "
"<mousebutton>desnim</mousebutton> klikom na namizje za kakršno koli "
"spreminjanje)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid "Application Menu"
msgstr "Meni aplikacij"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you prefer the traditional menu-style application launcher, change it by "
"<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> clicking on the menu button and selecting "
"<guimenuitem>Alternatives</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Če imate raje tradicionalni zaganjalnik aplikacij v obliki menija, ga "
"spremenite tako, da <mousebutton>desno</mousebutton> kliknete gumb menija in "
"izberete <guimenuitem>Alternative</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Application menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Meni aplikacij</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Application menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Meni aplikacij</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "Application Launcher Settings"
msgstr "Nastavitve zaganjalnika aplikacij"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to configure the application launcher, change it by "
"<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> clicking on the menu button and selecting "
"<guimenuitem>Configure Application Launcher</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite konfigurirati zaganjalnik aplikacij, ga spremenite tako, da "
"<mousebutton>desno</mousebutton> kliknete gumb menija in izberete "
"<guimenuitem>Konfiguracija zaganjalnika aplikacij</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Application launcher settings</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Nastavitve zaganjalnika aplikacij</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Application launcher settings</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Nastavitve zaganjalnika aplikacij</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid "Taskbar"
msgstr "Opravilna vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The taskbar is another widget on the panel. It shows an area for all open "
"windows on all desktops by default. You can make it show all open windows on "
"the current desktop only by checking <guimenuitem>Only show tasks from the "
"current desktop</guimenuitem> when you right click on the task manager, "
"between two windows. The size of the text on the taskbar items can be set in "
"&systemsettings; under the <menuchoice><guimenu>Appearance</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Fonts</guisubmenu> </menuchoice>. Right-clicking on the "
"taskbar brings the Settings dialog where you can choose several options to "
"customize your taskbar."
msgstr ""
"Opravilna vrstica je še en gradnik na plošči. Privzeto prikazuje območje za "
"vsa odprta okna na vseh namizjih. Prikaz vseh odprtih oken na trenutnem "
"namizju lahko omogočite tako, da ob desnem kliku na upravitelja opravil med "
"dvema oknoma potrdite <guimenuitem>Prikaži samo opravila s trenutnega "
"namizja</guimenuitem>. Velikost besedila na elementih opravilne vrstice "
"lahko nastavite v &systemsettings; pod <menuchoice><guimenu>Oblika</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Pisave</guisubmenu> </menuchoice>. Z desnim klikom na "
"opravilno vrstico odprete pogovorno okno Nastavitve, v katerem lahko "
"izberete več možnosti za prilagoditev opravilne vrstice."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here is a screenshot of the taskbar settings dialog"
msgstr "Tu je posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna nastavitev opravilne vrstice"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid "Taskbar settings dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno z nastavitvami opravilne vrstice"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid "System Tray"
msgstr "Sistemska vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another default panel item is the <application>System Tray</application>, "
"which is used by traditional applications and widgets as a dock. Right "
"clicking on the <application>System Tray</application> allows you to open "
"the settings dialog, where you can set entries to display and their "
"visibility."
msgstr ""
"Drugi privzeti element na plošči je <application>Sistemski pladenj</"
"application>, ki ga običajne aplikacije in gradniki uporabljajo kot dok. Z "
"desnim klikom na <application>Sistemska vrstica</application> lahko odprete "
"pogovorno okno z nastavitvami, v katerem lahko nastavite vnose, ki naj se "
"prikažejo, in njihovo vidnost."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>System Tray settings dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Pogovorno okno z nastavitvami sistemske vrstice</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>System Tray settings dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno z nastavitvami sistemske vrstice</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:287
#, no-c-format
msgid "Device Notifier"
msgstr "Obvestilo naprave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An icon located usually in the system tray is the <application>Device "
"Notifier</application>. Plug in a &USB; disk and a dialog will open that "
"allows you to open the device in &dolphin; or another associated application."
msgstr ""
"Ikona, ki se običajno nahaja v sistemski vrstici, je <application>Obvestilo "
"naprave</application>. Priključite disk &USB; in odprlo se bo pogovorno "
"okno, v katerem lahko odprete napravo v programu &dolphin; ali drugi "
"povezani aplikaciji."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:307
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <application>Device Notifier</application> is used for handling "
"pluggable devices such as &USB; pendrives (also called flash drives or thumb "
"drives), digital cameras, external &USB; hard drives, &etc; It also comes "
"into play when a medium such as a &CD; or DVD is loaded into an optical "
"drive."
msgstr ""
"Aplikacija <application>Obvestilo naprave</application> se uporablja za "
"ravnanje z napravami, ki jih je mogoče priključiti, kot so pendrivi "
"(imenovani tudi flash diski ali palčki), digitalni fotoaparati, zunanji "
"&USB; trdi diski &etc;; Uporablja se tudi, ko se v optični pogon naloži "
"medij, kot je &CD; ali DVD."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you plug in an external device, or load a new medium into a drive, the "
"<guilabel>Notifier</guilabel> window pops up (you can also open it "
"explicitly by clicking on its Panel icon.) It stays open while the cursor is "
"over it, otherwise it hides itself after a few seconds."
msgstr ""
"Ko priključite zunanjo napravo ali v pogon naložite nov medij, se prikaže "
"okno <guilabel>Obveščevalnik</guilabel> (odprete ga lahko tudi izrecno s "
"klikom na ikono na plošči). Odprt ostane, dokler je nad njim kazalec, sicer "
"se po nekaj sekundah skrije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Notifier</guilabel> window shows a list of all the devices it "
"currently knows about. Moving the mouse cursor over a device will highlight "
"how many possible actions are associated with that device."
msgstr ""
"Okno <guilabel>Obveščevalnik</guilabel> prikazuje seznam vseh naprav, ki jih "
"trenutno pozna. Če premaknete kazalec miške nad napravo, boste označili, "
"koliko možnih dejanj je povezanih s to napravo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking anywhere in the shaded box around the device name (but not on the "
"eject/unmount icon if present) expands the entry to show the list of "
"possible actions for that device. The set of actions depends on the device; "
"it is configurable from the <application>Device Notifier</application>'s "
"context menu or from the &systemsettings; modules <ulink url=\"help:/"
"kcontrol/solid-actions/index.html\">Device Actions</ulink> and <ulink url="
"\"help:/kcontrol/solid-device-automounter/index.html\">Removable Devices</"
"ulink>. Simply select one with the mouse or keyboard to launch that action."
msgstr ""
"S klikom kjer koli v osenčenem polju okoli imena naprave (vendar ne na ikono "
"za izmet/odstranitev, če je prisotna) razširite vnos in prikažete seznam "
"možnih dejanj za to napravo. Nabor ukrepov je odvisen od naprave; nastaviti "
"ga je mogoče v kontekstnem meniju <application>Obvestilo naprave</"
"application> ali v nastavitvah &systemsettings; modulih <ulink url=\"help:/"
"kcontrol/solid-actions/index.html\">Dejanja naprav</ulink> in <ulink url="
"\"help:/kcontrol/solid-device-automounter/index.html\">Odstranljive naprave</"
"ulink>. Enostavno ga izberite z miško ali tipkovnico, da zaženete to dejanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is also a small icon to the right of each entry showing whether that "
"device is currently accessible (or <emphasis>mounted</emphasis>) or not. "
"Only when a device is not mounted is it safe to physically disconnect it "
"from the computer. Clicking on the icon causes the device to be unmounted "
"and/or the medium to be ejected if it is currently mounted, and will mount "
"it if it is not. Note that unmounting/ejecting might fail if the device "
"still has open files on it, &eg; if a large file copy hasn't finished. In "
"most cases you can just wait a while and try again. When an unmounting has "
"succeeded, a success icon will be shown on the <application>Device Notifier</"
"application>'s icon."
msgstr ""
"Na desni strani vsakega vnosa je tudi majhna ikona, ki prikazuje, ali je "
"naprava trenutno dostopna (ali <emphasis>montirana</emphasis>) ali ne. "
"Napravo lahko fizično odklopite iz računalnika le, če ni nameščena. S klikom "
"na ikono se naprava odmontira in/ali medij izloči, če je trenutno nameščen, "
"če pa ni, se namesti. Upoštevajte, da lahko odstranitev/izmet ne uspe, če so "
"v napravi še vedno odprte datoteke, &eg; če se kopiranje velike datoteke še "
"ni končalo. V večini primerov lahko nekaj časa počakate in poskusite znova. "
"Ko je odstranjevanje uspešno, se na ikoni <application>Obvestilo naprave</"
"application> prikaže ikona uspeha."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hidden Items"
msgstr "Skriti predmeti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:335
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <application>System Tray</application> normally holds some more entries "
"like &klipper;, &kmix; &etc;"
msgstr ""
"<application>Sistemska vrstica</application> običajno vsebuje še nekaj "
"vnosov, kot so &klipper;, &kmix; &etc;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:338
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some of the default entries in the <application>System Tray</application> "
"are hidden to save space in the bar. To display these entries click on the "
"small white triangle <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"system-tray-up-arrow.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>, then use the &LMB; to launch a widget or the &RMB; to "
"open its settings dialog."
msgstr ""
"Nekateri privzeti vnosi v <application>Sistemska vrstica</application> so "
"skriti, da se prihrani prostor v vrstici. Za prikaz teh vnosov kliknite "
"majhen bel trikotnik <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"system-tray-up-arrow.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>, nato uporabite &LMB; za zagon gradnika ali &RMB; za "
"odprtje njegovega pogovornega okna za nastavitve."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid "Digital Clock"
msgstr "Digitalna ura"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The right-most &plasma; widget in the default panel holds the "
"<application>Digital Clock</application>. This clock can display the time in "
"different timezones as well as have its size changed. The clock will adjust "
"its font size to the area it is given by the surrounding containment (that "
"is the panel in this case). If you choose to display the date, this date "
"will be rendered using the <guimenuitem>Small font</guimenuitem> option from "
"the &systemsettings; <guilabel>Font</guilabel> dialog. The time will take "
"the rest of the space. So in the end, you'll choose yourself the amount of "
"information displayed, and if that fits. If you want to display more "
"information, make the panel larger or put the clock on the desktop where it "
"can grow freely."
msgstr ""
"Najbolj desno &plasma; gradnik na privzeti plošči vsebuje "
"<application>Digitalna ura</application>. Ta ura lahko prikazuje čas v "
"različnih časovnih pasovih in spreminja svojo velikost. Ura bo prilagodila "
"velikost pisave območju, ki ji ga zagotavlja okoliški prostor (v tem primeru "
"je to plošča). Če se odločite za prikaz datuma, bo ta datum prikazan z "
"uporabo možnosti <guimenuitem>Majhna pisava</guimenuitem> iz pogovornega "
"okna &systemsettings; <guilabel>Pisava</guilabel>. Čas bo zasedel preostali "
"prostor. Na koncu boste torej sami izbrali količino prikazanih informacij in "
"ali vam ustrezajo. Če želite prikazati več informacij, povečajte ploščo ali "
"postavite uro na namizje, kjer lahko prosto raste."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:364
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pager"
msgstr "Pozivnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An optional item on your panel is the <application>Pager</application>. It "
"allows you to switch between your virtual desktops. If you change the layout "
"of the <application>Pager</application> through the <guimenuitem>Number of "
"rows</guimenuitem> option, which will also affect the layout and animations "
"that are shown in &kwin;’s <guimenuitem>Desktop Grid</guimenuitem> effect. "
"For larger pagers, selecting <guimenuitem>Display windows icons</"
"guimenuitem> typically makes sense."
msgstr ""
"Izbirni element na plošči je <application>Pozivnik</application>. Omogoča "
"preklapljanje med navideznimi namizji. Če spremenite postavitev "
"<application>Pozivnika</application> z možnostjo <guimenuitem>Število "
"vrstic</guimenuitem>, bo to vplivalo tudi na postavitev in animacije, ki so "
"prikazane v učinku <guimenuitem>Mreža namizja</guimenuitem> &kwin;. Za večje "
"pozivnike je izbira možnosti <guimenuitem>Prikaz ikon oken</guimenuitem> "
"običajno smiselna."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:387
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Panel Toolbox"
msgstr "Orodjarna plošče"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your desktop is unlocked (you can do that by <mousebutton>right</"
"mousebutton> clicking on the desktop, or when no application has the focus, "
"with <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo>, "
"<keycap>L</keycap>), a small &plasma; logo will appear in the bottom right "
"corner in the panel. Click on this toolbox, and the panel controller opens."
msgstr ""
"Če je namizje odklenjeno (to lahko storite tako, da <mousebutton>desno</"
"mousebutton> kliknete na namizje, ali če nobena aplikacija nima fokusa, s "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo>, <keycap>L</"
"keycap>), se v spodnjem desnem kotu plošče pojavi majhen logotip &plasma;. "
"Kliknite na to orodjarno in odpre se krmilnik plošče."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:397
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Panel Settings</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Nastavitve plošče</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:403
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Panel Settings</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Nastavitve plošče</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The panel controller allows you to reposition, resize and realign the panel. "
"The &plasma; widgets living in this panel will adjust their size "
"automatically. &plasma; widgets have basic knowledge about sizing, provided "
"by the containment. They are programmed to take advantage of that size, and "
"inform the applet about how much space they possibly need. In the end, the "
"containment gives a possible size to the applets, the applets obey."
msgstr ""
"S krmilnikom plošče lahko spremenite položaj, velikost in postavitev plošče. "
"Gradniki &plasma;, ki živijo na tej plošči, bodo samodejno prilagodili svojo "
"velikost. &plasma; gradniki imajo osnovno znanje o velikosti, ki ga "
"zagotavlja vsebina. Programirani so tako, da izkoristijo to velikost in "
"obvestijo programček o tem, koliko prostora potrebujejo. Na koncu omejitev "
"jabolkom določi možno velikost, jabolka pa se ji podredijo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:418
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding Applets"
msgstr "Dodajanje programčkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:420
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unlock the desktop and you'll be able to add and remove &plasma; widgets "
"from panel or desktop. You add &plasma; widgets by simply dragging them "
"where you want them. <mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> click on an widget to "
"remove it. <screenshot> <screeninfo>Add Widgets</screeninfo> <mediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"add-widgets.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> <textobject> <phrase>Add Widgets</phrase> </textobject> </"
"mediaobject> </screenshot> The <guibutton>Get New Widgets</guibutton> button "
"allows you to add widgets you've previously downloaded and download new "
"&plasma; widgets. Currently it supports native &plasmagik; packages and some "
"&Mac; OS&nbsp;X dashboard widgets. Widgets you install this way can then be "
"accessed just like regular, preinstalled widgets."
msgstr ""
"Odklenite namizje in lahko dodajate in odstranjujete gradnike s plošče ali "
"namizja. Gradnike &plasma; dodajate tako, da jih preprosto povlečete, kamor "
"želite. <mousebutton>Desno</mousebutton> kliknite na gradnik, da ga "
"odstranite. <screenshot> <screeninfo>Dodaj gradnike</screeninfo> "
"<mediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"add-widgets.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> <phrase>Dodaj gradnike</phrase> </"
"textobject> </mediaobject> </screenshot> Gumb <guibutton>Pridobi nove "
"gradnike</guibutton> vam omogoča dodajanje gradnikov, ki ste jih predhodno "
"naložili, in prenos novih gradnikov &plasma;. Trenutno podpira izvirne "
"pakete &plasmagik; in nekatere pripomočke za nadzorno ploščo &Mac; OS&nbsp;"
"X. Do tako nameščenih gradnikov lahko dostopate kot do običajnih, vnaprej "
"nameščenih gradnikov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:446
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Desktop"
msgstr "Namizje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:448
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The desktop is in fact another containment. One that does not put size "
"constraints on the applets. Applets can be moved and sized freely. On the "
"unlocked desktop, &plasma; widgets will show a frame when you move the mouse "
"over them. This applet handle allows you to move, resize, relocate and "
"realign the panel. It also allows you to drag &plasma; widgets on the "
"desktop. The buttons in the corner are used to resize, rotate configure and "
"remove the applet. When rotated, a &plasma; widget will act magnetic towards "
"12 o'clock, so it is easy to get them back into sensible position. By "
"default, most applets keep their aspect ratio when they are being resized. "
"If you want to freely resize an applet, hold the &Ctrl; key pressed while "
"resizing."
msgstr ""
"Namizje je pravzaprav še en prostor za zadrževanje. Takšna, ki ne omejuje "
"velikosti programčkov. Majhne programe lahko poljubno premikate in določate "
"njihovo velikost. Na odklenjenem namizju bodo gradniki &plasma; prikazali "
"okvir, ko se z miško premaknete nad njih. S tem ročajem lahko premikate, "
"spreminjate velikost, prestavljate in poravnavate ploščo. Omogoča tudi "
"vlečenje &plasma; gradnikov na namizju. Gumbi v kotu se uporabljajo za "
"spreminjanje velikosti, vrtenje, konfiguriranje in odstranjevanje "
"programčkov. Pri vrtenju bo pripomoček &plasma; deloval magnetno proti 12. "
"uri, zato ga je enostavno vrniti v smiseln položaj. Večina majhnih programov "
"med spreminjanjem velikosti privzeto ohrani svoje razmerje stranic. Če "
"želite poljubno spremeniti velikost programčka, med spreminjanjem velikosti "
"držite pritisnjeno tipko &Ctrl;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:461
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Right clicking on the desktop also offers you to configure aspects such as "
"the wallpaper and the layout used, and the mouse actions. It offers to "
"download new wallpapers through &knewstuff;."
msgstr ""
"Z desnim klikom na namizje lahko tudi konfigurirate vidike, kot so ozadje, "
"uporabljena postavitev in dejanja z miško. Ponuja prenos novih ozadij prek "
"&knewstuff;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:466
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the <guilabel>Tweaks</guilabel> page you can configure to hide the "
"desktop Toolbox and adjust the widget handling."
msgstr ""
"Na strani <guilabel>Popravki</guilabel> lahko konfigurirate skrivanje "
"namiznega orodjarne in prilagodite ravnanje z gradniki."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:471
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Desktop Settings</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Nastavitve namizja</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:477
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Desktop Settings</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Nastavitve namizja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the &plasma; theme or download a new one through &knewstuff; open "
"the <menuchoice><guimenu>Appearance</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Desktop Theme</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> page in the &systemsettings;."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti temo &plasma; ali prenesti novo prek &knewstuff; "
"odprite stran <menuchoice><guimenu>Oblika</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Tema "
"namizja</guimenuitem></menuchoice> v &systemsettings;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:486
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With open applications, it quickly gets hard to see the &plasma; widgets on "
"your desktop. The <emphasis role=\"bold\">Dashboard</emphasis> gets those "
"&plasma; widgets in front of you, much like the <guilabel>Peek at Desktop</"
"guilabel> functionality you are used to from traditional desktops."
msgstr ""
"Z odprtimi aplikacijami hitro težko vidite pripomočke na namizju. <emphasis "
"role=\"bold\">Armaturna plošča</emphasis> pred vas postavi te &plasma; "
"gradnike, podobno kot funkcionalnost <guilabel>Pokukaj na namizje</"
"guilabel>, ki ste je vajeni iz običajnih namizij."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:496
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Folder View</title>"
msgstr "<title>Pogled mape</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:497
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Folder View</guilabel> widget is used to display entries like "
"folders or files from a folder, by default from <filename class=\"directory"
"\">$<envar>HOME</envar>/Desktop</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Gradnik <guilabel>Pogled mape</guilabel> se uporablja za prikaz vnosov, kot "
"so mape ali datoteke iz mape, privzeto iz <filename class=\"directory\">"
"$<envar>HOME</envar>/Namizje</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:500
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can choose to view either all files, or filter either by specific "
"regular expressions (&eg;, all files with a certain extension) or by file "
"type (&eg; just images)."
msgstr ""
"Izbirate lahko med pregledovanjem vseh datotek ali filtriranjem po določenih "
"regularnih izrazih (&eg;, vse datoteke z določeno končnico) ali po vrsti "
"datoteke (&eg; samo slike)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:503
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This widget also supports basic file management properties (moving, copying, "
"cutting and pasting for example), and you can have as many as you want on "
"your desktop."
msgstr ""
"Ta gradnik podpira tudi osnovne lastnosti upravljanja datotek (na primer "
"premikanje, kopiranje, rezanje in lepljenje), na namizju pa jih imate lahko "
"poljubno veliko."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:508
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Folder View</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pogled mape</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Folder View</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogled mape</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:519
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you select the layout <guilabel>Folder View</guilabel> in the "
"<guilabel>Desktop Settings</guilabel> you can use one Folder View as the "
"whole desktop, effectively replicating the \"old style\" desktop paradigm."
msgstr ""
"Če v <guilabel>Nastavitve namizja</guilabel> izberete postavitev "
"<guilabel>Pogled mape</guilabel>, lahko en pogled mape uporabite kot celotno "
"namizje, s čimer učinkovito ponovite paradigmo namizja v \"starem slogu\"."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:525
#, no-c-format
msgid "&krunner;"
msgstr "&krunner;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:526
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&krunner; is a versatile mini command-line. You can use it to start "
"applications, open web pages, access bookmarks, search through your desktop "
"data, calculate short equations, and many more. Pressing <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Alt;&Space;</keycombo> or <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keysym>F2</keysym></keycombo> opens the &krunner; dialog. You just start "
"typing and &krunner; will start searching matches as soon as you've entered "
"more than two characters. You can open the settings dialog to learn about "
"&krunner;’s functionality, provided by plugins. You can navigate through the "
"matches using the tab and arrow keys."
msgstr ""
"&krunner; je vsestranska mini ukazna vrstica. Z njim lahko zaženete "
"aplikacije, odprete spletne strani, dostopate do zaznamkov, iščete po "
"podatkih na namizju, izračunate kratke enačbe in še veliko več. S pritiskom "
"na <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Space;</keycombo> ali <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>F2</keysym></keycombo> se odpre pogovorno okno "
"&krunner;. Samo začnete tipkati in &krunner; bo začel iskati zadetke takoj, "
"ko boste vnesli več kot dva znaka. Odprite pogovorno okno z nastavitvami in "
"se seznanite s funkcijami &krunner;, ki jih zagotavljajo vtičniki. Po tekmah "
"se lahko pomikate s tabulatorjem in smernimi tipkami."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:539
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&krunner; dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&krunner; dialog</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:545
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&krunner; dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&krunner; dialog</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:550
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"krunner-"
"configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> button "
"to open the <guilabel>KRunner</guilabel> &systemsettings; module and "
"configure where and what to search for in &krunner;."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite gumb <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"krunner-"
"configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject>, da "
"odprete modul <guilabel>KRunner</guilabel> &systemsettings; ter "
"konfigurirate, kje in kaj naj se išče v &krunner;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:555
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&krunner; supports <quote>Desktop Actions</quote> which are additional "
"actions an application can offer to perform common actions or jump directly "
"to a certain task from Task Manager. Common examples are <guilabel>Open New "
"Incognito Window</guilabel> to open your browser directly in private mode, "
"<guilabel>Compose Email</guilabel> without launching the full-fledged email "
"client first or the actions provided by &spectacle;:"
msgstr ""
"&krunner; podpira <quote>Dejanja namizja</quote>, ki so dodatna dejanja, ki "
"jih lahko aplikacija ponudi za izvajanje običajnih dejanj ali neposreden "
"preskok na določeno opravilo iz Upravitelja opravil. Pogosti primeri so "
"<guilabel>Odpri novo okno brez beleženja zgodovine</guilabel> za neposredno "
"odprtje brskalnika v zasebnem načinu, <guilabel>Sestavite e-pošto</"
"guilabel>, ne da bi najprej zagnali polnopravni e-poštni odjemalec, ali "
"dejanja, ki jih zagotavlja &spectacle;:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:563
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&krunner; Desktop Actions</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&krunner; Dejavnosti namizja</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:569
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&krunner; Desktop Actions</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&krunner; Dejavnosti namizja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:574
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you press the &Down; key in an empty &krunner; a history of the recent "
"entities is shown. After invoking a search result, its query will move to "
"the top, so repeatedly used commands never fall out of the list."
msgstr ""
"Če pritisnete tipko &Down; v praznem &krunner;, se prikaže zgodovina zadnjih "
"entitet. Po priklicu rezultata iskanja se njegova poizvedba premakne na vrh, "
"tako da večkrat uporabljeni ukazi nikoli ne izpadejo s seznama."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:578
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Remove single entries from the list using the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"remove.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> button or clear the complete "
"history in the &krunner; settings."
msgstr ""
"Posamezne vnose s seznama odstranite z gumbom "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"remove.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> ali počistite celotno zgodovino "
"v nastavitvah &krunner;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:583
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to know what is going on on your system, pressing <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Esc;</keycombo> gives you quick access to a list of "
"windows and processes, with options to monitor their output and kill "
"processes."
msgstr ""
"Če želite vedeti, kaj se dogaja v sistemu, lahko s pritiskom <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Esc;</keycombo> hitro dostopate do seznama oken in "
"procesov z možnostmi za spremljanje njihovega izpisa in ubijanje procesov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:591
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Activities</title>"
msgstr "<title>Dejavnosti</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:593
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The desktop toolbox, accessed via the upper left corner has a button for "
"displaying your activities, of which &plasma; allows you to have more than "
"one. Basically, that is multiple desktop containments hosting multiple sets "
"of &plasma; widgets. Display the <quote>Activities</quote> bar, select one "
"of the predefined activities or choose <guilabel>Create Activity</guilabel> "
"to create a new containment, select your new containment and customize "
"suiting your taste. &plasma;’s activities and &kwin;’s desktop grid are "
"similar in that respect, but there is a fundamental difference. While "
"virtual desktop are used to group and organize windows, &plasma;’s "
"activities are used to group and organize &plasma; widgets. This way, you "
"can switch between activities and have relevant &plasma; widgets supporting "
"the task you are currently trying to accomplish. You can create a "
"<quote>Free time</quote> activity, with comic strips, a puzzle and other "
"&plasma; widgets, and a <quote>Work</quote> activity, with relevant "
"<acronym>RSS</acronym> feeds, calculator and calendar, for example."
msgstr ""
"Orodjarna namizja, do katere dostopate preko zgornjega levega kota, ima gumb "
"za prikaz vaših dejavnosti, med katerimi je &plasma; vam omogoča, da imate "
"več kot enega. V bistvu je to več namiznih vsebnikov, ki gostijo več nizov "
"&plasma; pripomočki. Prikažite vrstico <quote>Dejavnosti</quote>, izberite "
"eno od vnaprej določenih dejavnosti ali izberite <guilabel>Ustvari "
"dejavnost</guilabel>, da ustvarite nov vsebnik, izberite svoj novi vsebnik "
"in ga prilagodite svojemu okusu. Dejavnosti &plasma; in namizna mreža &kwin; "
"so v tem pogledu podobne, vendar obstaja bistvena razlika. Medtem ko se "
"navidezno namizje uporablja za združevanje in organiziranje oken, se "
"dejavnosti &plasma; uporabljajo za združevanje in organiziranje &plasma; "
"pripomočki. Na ta način lahko preklapljate med dejavnostmi in imate ustrezne "
"&plasma; gradniki, ki podpirajo nalogo, ki jo trenutno poskušate opraviti. "
"Ustvarite lahko dejavnost <quote>Prosti čas</quote> s stripi, sestavljanko "
"in drugimi &plasma; pripomočki in dejavnost <quote>Delo</quote> z ustreznimi "
"viri <acronym>RSS</acronym>, kalkulatorjem in koledarjem, na primer."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:609
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To delete an activity, press the <guibutton>Stop Activity</guibutton> button "
"on <quote>Activities</quote> bar (press <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo> then <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> to open this bar) then click the red 'X' (or "
"press <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo> then "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo>) and confirm "
"the deletion."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izbrisati dejavnost, pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Ustavi dejavnost</"
"guibutton> v vrstici <quote>Dejavnosti</quote> (pritisnite <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo> nato <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Alt;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> za odprtje te vrstice), nato kliknite "
"rdeči 'X' (ali pritisnite <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>D</"
"keycap></keycombo> nato <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>R</keycap></"
"keycombo>) in potrdite izbris."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:622
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shortcuts"
msgstr "Bližnjice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:624
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most of &plasma;’s functionality is also accessible through keyboard "
"shortcuts. The various combinations should be pressed in sequence, that is "
"for example <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo>, "
"<keycap>A</keycap> means: Press &Alt; and <keycap>D</keycap>, release and "
"press <keycap>A</keycap>."
msgstr ""
"Večina funkcij programa &plasma; je na voljo tudi z bližnjicami na "
"tipkovnici. Različne kombinacije je treba pritiskati zaporedno, torej na "
"primer <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo>, "
"<keycap>A</keycap> pomeni: Pritisnite &Alt; in <keycap>D</keycap>, sprostite "
"in pritisnite <keycap>A</keycap>."

